value.0: Dogma of Set: The ends justify the means, and life is a struggle to be won by the powerful and the ruthless. Loyalty to one’s comrades is admirable as long as it advances the cause of Set, and in the end, when Set accedes to his rightful throne, those that have served him well will be justly rewarded. Destroy the clergies of Horus-Re and Osiris, thus accelerating Set’s establishment at his rightful place as the god-king of Mulhorand, and spread the cult of Set throughout the world. Sacrifice both wealth and sentients to Set.
